    "text": {
      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Rhys Rustad-Elliott</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:202px;\"><a href=\"/File:RhysRustadElliott.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/3/39/RhysRustadElliott.jpg\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" class=\"thumbimage\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:RhysRustadElliott.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Rhys Rustad-Elliott  <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Rhys Rustad-Elliott</b>,<br />\t\na Canadian software engineer with an <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Undergraduate_degree\">undergraduate degree</a> in computer science from <a href=\"/University_of_Toronto\" title=\"University of Toronto\">University of Toronto</a>, and computer chess programmer.\nHe is author of the <a href=\"/UCI\" title=\"UCI\">UCI</a> compliant <a href=\"/Category:Open_Source\" title=\"Category:Open Source\">open source chess engine</a> <a href=\"/Shallow_Blue\" title=\"Shallow Blue\">Shallow Blue</a>.\nOn his blog, Rhys Rustad-Elliott  gave an excellent description of <a href=\"/Magic_Bitboards\" title=\"Magic Bitboards\">Magic Bitboards</a> as used in Shallow Blue <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Postings\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Postings</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Postings\">Postings</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Rhys_Rustad-Elliott&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Postings\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://medium.com/hootsuite-engineering/a-gentle-introduction-to-object-oriented-programming-in-javascript-a46f25de8b07\">A Gentle Introduction to Object-Oriented Programming in JavaScript</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Rhys Rustad-Elliott</a>, August 30, 2016</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://rhysre.net/fast-chess-move-generation-with-magic-bitboards.html\">Fast Chess Move Generation With Magic Bitboards</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Rhys Rustad-Elliott</a>, January 15, 2019</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Rhys_Rustad-Elliott&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/rhysrustadelliott/\">Rhys Rustad-Elliott | LinkedIn</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/GunshipPenguin\">Rhys Rustad-Elliott · GitHub</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://rhysre.net/\">Rhys Rustad-Elliott</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://harthousechess.com/2018/02/05/chess-movie-night-lecture-humans-v-engines/\">Rhys Rustad-Elliot introduces “Shallow Blue” and reflects on “Alpha Go”, Computers and AI!</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://harthousechess.com/\">Hart House Chess Club</a>, February 05, 2018</li></ul>\n<dl><dd> Interview with Rhys Rustad-Elliott, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://harthousechess.com/\">Hart House Chess Club</a>, February 02, 2018, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/YouTube\">YouTube</a> Video </dd>\n<dd> <div class='embedvideo ev_inline ev_top autoResize' style=' width: 646px;'><div class='embedvideowrap' style='width: 640px;'><iframe src=\"//www.youtube.com/embed/jpTfY4lxqNY?\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe></div></div></dd></dl>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Rhys_Rustad-Elliott&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://rhysre.net/pages/about.html\">Rhys Rustad-Elliott - About</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://rhysre.net/fast-chess-move-generation-with-magic-bitboards.html\">Fast Chess Move Generation With Magic Bitboards</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Rhys Rustad-Elliott</a>, January 15, 2019</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">Up one level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260301041105\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.012 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.013 